main event: Witnesses reported seeing objects in the sky on multiple occasions in Walpole, Massachusetts, including a triangular-shaped object on September 9, 1965.
interesting points: One witness observed two similar luminous objects with an oval shape moving slowly in the sky for about 20-25 minutes., Another witness saw a triangular-shaped object that was brilliantly lighted and moved rapidly across the sky., The triangular object was described as the most beautiful blue-green color ever seen by the witness., The sighting on September 9 was claimed to travel from horizon to horizon in just 8 seconds., The report is part of Project Blue Book, which investigated unidentified flying objects.
sighted object: two luminous objects and a triangular-shaped object
witness description: witnesses observed the objects on different occasions with detailed descriptions.
